Label.Text: **NOTE: There isn't a way to error check. If you put something in a slot that isn't actually in the bank (i.e. putting something in slot 9 instead of an 8 slot bag), then when you zone, the item will appear on your cursor. If you've put multiple things in the wrong slot then they'll all go to your cursor but only the top most item will be kept...all others will be LOST.**
